&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;üìà In addition to our cash compensation, we offer equity (because when we succeed as a company, we want you to succeed, too) and generous&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;text-decoration: none; color: var(--link-color);&quot; href=&quot;https://handbook.sourcegraph.com/benefits-pay-perks/benefits-perks/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;perks &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
