&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre looking for a motivated and results-driven &lt;strong&gt;General Accountant&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Finance team. The ideal candidate is eager to be part of a fast-growing tech company and help drive innovation. In this role, you‚Äôll support RevOps and manage key accounting functions, ensuring efficient AP and AR processes while minimizing cash burn and revenue leakage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You‚Äôll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
